D-dimer and CRP levels are elevated prior to antiretroviral
treatment in patients who develop IRIS
Brian O. Porter, M.D., Ph.D., M.P.H., National Institutes of Health (NIH), National Institute of Allergy & Infectious Diseases (NIAID)
G. Laissa Ouedraogo, M.D., M.P.H.&T.M., SAIC, National Institute of Allergy & Infectious Diseases (NIAID)
